<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''心搏停止'''（'''英文'''：Cardiac arrest）或稱為心臟停止'''、'''[[心跳停止|心跳停止]]，是[[心臟|心臟]]因不能夠有效收縮，而導致[[循环系统|血液循環]]停止的現象<ref name=NIH2016What/>，症狀包含{{le|意識喪失|Unconsciousness|喪失意識}}、{{le|呼吸驟止|respiratory arrest|呼吸異常或中止}}<ref name=Fie2009/><ref name=NIH2016Sign/>，有些患者在心搏驟止前還會[[胸痛|胸痛]]、[[呼吸困難|呼吸困難]]，以及[[恶心|恶心]]等症狀<ref name="NIH2016Sign">{{cite web|title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of Sudden Cardiac Arrest?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/signs|website=NHLBI|accessdate=16 August 2016|date=June 22, 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827190624/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/signs|archivedate=27 August 2016}}</ref>心搏停止後若無獲得治療，一般會在數分鐘內[[死亡|死亡]]<ref name="NIH2016What">{{cite web|title=What Is Sudden Cardiac Arrest?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda|website=NHLBI|accessdate=16 August 2016|date=June 22, 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728031608/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda|archivedate=28 July 2016}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
最常造成心搏驟止的原因是[[冠狀動脈疾病|冠心病]]<ref name=NIH2016Ca/>，其他較少見的原因包含[[出血|大出血]]、缺氧、[[低鉀血症|血鉀極低]]、[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]，以及過度運動<ref name=NIH2016Ca/>。有些遺傳疾病如[[長QT綜合症|長QT症]]也會增加心搏驟停的風險<ref name=NIH2016Ca/>，在心搏驟停之前，最常先觀察到有[[心室顫動|心室顫動]]的現象<ref name="NIH2016Ca">{{cite web|title=What Causes Sudden Cardiac Arrest?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/causes|website=NHLBI|accessdate=16 August 2016|date=June 22, 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728042233/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/causes|archivedate=28 July 2016}}</ref>。確診方法為無心搏<ref name=Fie2009/>值得注意的是，[[心肌梗死|心肌梗塞]]可能導致心搏停止，但這兩者並不相同<ref name=NIH2016What/>。

<!-- Treatment and prognosis -->
預防方法包含不抽菸、運動，以及維持體重在理想的範圍內<ref name=NIH2016Pre/>。治療方法為立即進行[[心肺复苏|心肺復甦術]]。若為可電擊復律心律（shockable rhythm），則進行[[去顫|去顫]]<ref name="NIH2016Tx">{{cite web|title=How Is Sudden Cardiac Arrest Treated?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/treatment|website=NHLBI|accessdate=16 August 2016|date=June 22, 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827184130/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/treatment|archivedate=27 August 2016}}</ref>若成功恢復心跳，{{le|目標體溫管理|Targeted Temperature Management}}也有助於改善結果<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Therapeutic hypothermia after cardiac arrest: A systematic review/meta-analysis exploring the impact of expanded criteria and targeted temperature|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27521472|last=Schenone|first=Aldo L.|last2=Cohen|first2=Aaron|date=11 2016|journal=Resuscitation|doi=10.1016/j.resuscitation.2016.07.238|volume=108|pages=102–110|issn=1873-1570|pmid=27521472|last3=Patarroyo|first3=Gabriel|last4=Harper|first4=Logan|last5=Wang|first5=XiaoFeng|last6=Shishehbor|first6=Mehdi H.|last7=Menon|first7=Venu|last8=Duggal|first8=Abhijit|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224231112/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27521472/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|植入型心臟去顫器|Implantable cardioverter-defibrillator}}也能減少日後復發致死的危險<ref name="NIH2016Pre">{{cite web|title=How Can Death Due to Sudden Cardiac Arrest Be Prevented?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/prevention|website=NHLBI|accessdate=16 August 2016|date=June 22, 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827200432/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/prevention|archivedate=27 August 2016}}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology and history -->
在[[美國|美國]]，醫院之外心臟驟停的發生率約為每年萬分之13（32萬6000例）<ref name=AHA2015Part4/>，院內心臟停止人數則約20萬9000例<ref name="AHA2015Part4"/>。心臟驟停的機會隨年齡增加<ref name=NIH2016Risk/>，其中男性較女性為多<ref name="NIH2016Risk">{{cite web|title=Who Is at Risk for Sudden Cardiac Arrest?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/atrisk|website=NHLBI|accessdate=16 August 2016|date=June 22, 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823231651/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/scda/atrisk|archivedate=23 August 2016}}</ref>，存活比例約為8%<ref name=Adam2012/>，且許多人留有明顯[[身心障礙|後遺症]]<ref name=Adam2012/>。許多美國電視劇播報心搏停止的存活率67%，這是不正確的<ref name="Adam2012">{{cite book|last1=Adams|first1=James G.|title=Emergency Medicine: Clinical Essentials (Expert Consult – Online)|date=2012|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=1455733946|page=1771|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rpoH-KYE93IC&pg=PA1771|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905133735/https://books.google.com/books?id=rpoH-KYE93IC&pg=PA1771|archivedate=2017-09-05}}</ref>。
